frontmatter.title: EyeSea
frontmatter.tools: ASP.NET, Ajax, Google Map and Map Suite
frontmatter.intro: A Vessel Tracking system for monitoring AIS + IMO, call sign, name, tonnage, and other vessel data at a glance. Access built-in predictive analytics to see past, present and future vessel information
